name: Bing Web Search
title: Bing Web Search
description: An AI service from Microsoft Azure that enables safe, ad-free, location-aware search for your users, surfacing relevant information from web results, images, local businesses, news, videos, and visuals.

endpoints.name: Web Search
endpoints.description: The Bing Web Search API enables you to integrate Bing's search capabilities in your applications. By sending search queries with the API, you can get relevant webpages, images, videos, news and more.
